data.description: Welcome to this stunning villa in Lake St Louis, a community that offers you a resort-style living with lakes, boating, fishing, clubhouse, pool and more. This villa features 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, with a spacious interior. You will love the vaulted ceilings, gas fireplace, and dining space in the Great Room. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with a planning desk, plenty of cabinet space, and a large pantry. The main floor also has a laundry room and a 2 car garage for your convenience. The master suite has a walk-in closet and a private bathroom with a double vanity and a step in shower. The second bedroom and bathroom are also on the main floor, perfect for guests or family. The lower level is finished, with a 3rd bedroom, a full bathroom, a living room, and enough space for an office or a hobby area.   This villa offers carefree living, with lawn care and snow removal included in the monthly fee. Don't miss this opportunity to own this beautiful villa in Lake St Louis!
